<html id="html-block-html" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en" lang="en"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="/common--theme/base/css/html-block.css"/></head><body><span style="font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:0.80em">It is regretful to announce that in two weeks time, we will need to shut down Wikidot. We thank the community for sticking with us for all these years, though we do understand that you may have lots of questions regarding the nature of why we are choosing to shut down after a <span id="years"></span> year run.</span><script>var dStart = new Date('2006-08-01 00:00');var dCurrent = new Date();document.getElementById("years").innerHTML = dCurrent.getYear() - dStart.getYear();</script><script type="text/javascript" src="/common--javascript/html-block-iframe.js"></script></body></html>